These files define the roles of the domains used in the sNow! HPC suite.
Developed by Jordi Blasco <jordi.blasco@hpcnow.com>

The roles are shell scripts which relies on xen-create-image and sNow! 
enviroment to build the final domain images.

If you wish to contribute in sNow! by includig new roles to the sNow! Tools,
please consider to use the provided template available in :
-->  etc/role.d/snow_reference_template
and document them in the man page of snow.conf (roles subsection). 

For more information, visit the official website : www.hpcnow.com/snow
